              "description": "Project Name: RGM - iOS: GIM App : 2018 - April\r\n\r\nStart Date: 2017/04/01\r\nEnd Date: 2017/04/30\r\n\r\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nMan Hours:  44.1 man-days\r\nInvestment: 1,021,016 JPY\r\n\r\nReturn : 90,876,146 JPY/year\r\n\r\nBU Priority : - \r\n\r\nDescription:\r\n# Deep Link Facebook app with Mall web pages to App native screens.\r\n# Investigate contents load latency of Cart&Checkout web pages to find improvement points.\r\n# Investigate contents load latency of CWD Contents to find improvement points.\r\n# Investigate contents load latency of Mall Web contents to find improvement points.\r\n# Display \"List Price\" in addition to sales price in <Product Listing> screens.\r\n# Display search results by respecting the language used in search keywords.\r\n# Display Shop Name in English\r\n\r\nQuick_guide check : Done",
