              "customfield_19802": "<div class=\"aui-message info\"><span class=\"aui-icon icon-info\"></span>\r\n<b> <font color=\"E60000\">To complete your request, please click “Create” button down below.</font></b>\r\n<li>If you see an error message on this screen, please modify it from this screen(JIRA), not from previous page(Confluence). \r\n<li>When you have an attachment, please upload the file from <b>“Attachment”</b> field in the <b>“Common Information for Request”</b> section. \r\n<li><font color=\"E60000\">Please do <b>NOT</b> click “Back” button on your browser, otherwise you will lose all information you typed. </font>\r\n<li>We will contact you within 2 business days after receiving your request. \r\n</div>",
              "customfield_19804": "<div class=\"aui-message info\"><span class=\"aui-icon icon-info\"></span>\r\nPlease fill in <b>\"Description\"</b> for user's information with all details below described.\r\n<br>\r\n<h4>1. Employment Type\r\n<h6>Please select the type as following,\r\n<li><h5> Joined(入社)\r\n<li><h5> Retirement(退職)\r\n<li><h5> Change (変更)\r\n<li><h5> Excluded(対象外)\r\n<h4>2. Employment Name\r\n<h6>Please type the name.\r\n<h4>Employment Name (furigana)</h4> \r\n<h6>Please type the name in \"furigana\".\r\n<h4>Email </h4> \r\n<h6>Please type the email address.\r\n<h4>Employee Type</h4>\r\n<h6>Please select the type as following,\r\n<li><h5> Regular Employee(正社員)\r\n<li><h5> Contract Employee(契約社員)\r\n<li><h5> Subcontractor(業務委託者)\r\n<li><h5> Temporary Staff(派遣社員)\r\n<li><h5> Temporary Staff(派遣社員)\r\n<h4>Supplier </h4> \r\n<h6>Please state it, only if <i>Employee Type is Subcontractor</i>.\r\n<h4>Section(Lv3)/Group(Lv4)/Team(Lv5)</h4>\r\n<h6>Please state the belonging department, following the order above.\r\n<h4>Authority Group</h4> \r\n<h6>Please select type for each user from following,\r\n<li><h5> Manager(マネジメント)\r\n<li><h5> Leader(リーダー)\r\n<li><h5> Subcontractor(業務委託者)\r\n<li><h5> Internal member(社内メンバー)\r\n<li><h5> External Leader(社外リーダー)\r\n<li><h5> External member(社外メンバー)\r\n<br>\r\n</div>",
              "customfield_19805": null,
              "customfield_19800": "<div class=\"aui-message info\"><span class=\"aui-icon icon-info\"></span>\r\n<b> Create a new issue</b> from <a href=\"https://confluence.dev.rakuten.com/confluence/x/YwBAFw\" target=\"_blank\"><b>here</b></a>.\r\n<BR>Please check it, you will see the Request Form. \r\n<BR>According to the guide, fill in the form, and then click <b>\"Request send to JIRA\"</b>.\r\n<BR>Moved to JIRA screen, click <b>Create</b> after you input information.\r\n</div>",
              "customfield_19801": "<div class=\"aui-message info\"><span class=\"aui-icon icon-info\"></span>\r\n<b> Create a new issue</b> from <a href=\"https://confluence.dev.rakuten.com/confluence/x/e_sqAg\" target=\"_blank\"><b>here</b></a>.\r\n<BR>Please check it, you will see the Request Form. \r\n<BR>According to the guide, fill in the form, and then click <b>\"Create a ticket on RDCS-WR(JIRA)\"</b>.\r\n<BR>Moved to JIRA screen, click <b>Create</b> after you input information.\r\n</div>",
